<plot>After being released from jail, it seems that Nontas, Giorgos and Christos (Stefanos is no longer part of their company) have not changed a bit. While trying to rape a teenage girl at a hill, they accidentally kill her. Her 2 sisters swear to take revenge and go after them. After investigating, they finally find them, seduce each one of them and execute them one by one, using a straight razor, a knife and a pair of scissors. In the end, it appears that they actually take pleasure in killing them. The film features many "flashback" sequenses taken from part 1.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?207567</url></doc>
